data.description: This beautiful 3 bedroom, 2.5 bath home is an excellent investment for any family within a thriving Katy area. This home already comes with quartz counter tops, a fireplace, hardwood flooring in the dining/living room areas, and even faux wood blinds throughout the house. Newly renovated in 2022, the luxury style kitchen comes with beautiful 42-inch shaker cabinets along with modern appliances. The home boasts a new HVAC system placed in 2023, with radiant barrier and new insulation blown into the attic in 2022. Roofing is only 7 years old with updated inspections. Windows were upgraded to a more energy efficient type, which greatly aided energy conservation. The master bathroom showcases the same luxury style theme that matches the kitchen, with a jacuzzi tub and standing shower. Just minutes away from all major highways surrounding Katy, this home is nestled within the Sundown Glen community, which makes for the perfect commute to work, schools, restaurants, and shopping centers.
